                                                                                              SA-08(25)       SECURITY AND PRIVACY ENGINEERING PRINCIPLES | ECONOMIC SECURITY
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              SA-08(25)_ODP         systems or system components that implement the security design principle of
                                                                                                                                    economic security are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-08(25)             <SA-08(25)_ODP systems or system components> implement the security design
                                                                                                                                    principle of economic security.

